title: Russia & Turkey-brokered Syria ceasefire has more chances than any other – UN Syria envoy
text:
Russia & Turkey-brokered Syria ceasefire has more chances than any other – UN Syria envoy Published time: 19 Feb, 2017 11:09 Edited time: 19 Feb, 2017 11:13 UN Special Envoy Staffan de Mistura has praised the joint efforts of Russia and Turkey to broker peace in Syria, and has urged the international community to support it.
